00:00:05,439 --> 00:00:06,519
Good afternoon, ma'am.

2
00:00:06,559 --> 00:00:09,759
My name is Mike and I'm selling subscriptions to all sorts of periodicals.

3
00:00:10,279 --> 00:00:10,820
No, thank you.

4
00:00:10,880 --> 00:00:11,580
I'm not interested.

5
