9
00:00:27,320 --> 00:00:30,160
Wow, well, that would be kind of useful.

10
00:00:30,899 --> 00:00:32,460
Do you have any other cooking magazines?

11
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:33,460
Sure do.

12
00:00:33,719 --> 00:00:39,500
