13
00:00:39,859 --> 00:00:41,159
Wow, this is nice.

14
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:44,060
Okay, sign me up for both publications.

15
00:00:44,539 --> 00:00:45,539
You mentioned you have a dog.

16
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:50,820
Most pet owners sign up for this weekly newsletter that has information on dog care, pet shops, and even pet sitters.

17
00:00:51,079 --> 00:00:52,679
That's exactly what I needed.

18
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,060
What else do you have?

19
00:00:54,259 --> 00:00:55,200
Well, I also have...

20
